  "_comment": "SHARED SPEC for booking totals — the single source of truth for the MATH, consumed by BOTH the backend engine (bookings/services/totals.py, via bookings/test_totals.py) and the frontend mirror (lib/quoteTotals.ts, via lib/quoteTotals.test.ts). Each case feeds food_total + line items (each with a precomputed signed line_total; discounts are negative) + tax_rate (decimal fraction) and asserts the resulting subtotal/tax_amount/total. food_total already includes any additional meals. Tax applies to the WHOLE subtotal (food + all line items) — there is no per-line taxable/non-taxable split. Change the rule => update this file => BOTH engine tests must conform. See docs/CALCULATION_PARITY.md.",
